data.description: Charming & Spacious with Elegant details throughout! This 3 bed, 2 full bath home boasts soaring ceilings, covers nearly 2,000 sqft, includes a private screened in pool, showstopping stone fireplace & a wonderfully designed open-floor plan! Wood look tile spans the majority of the flooring in the home topped with crown molding, wainscoting & tray ceilings to add exquisite touches. The eat-in kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & travertine tile backsplash. The master suite is HUGE & stuns with a walk-in closet & spa-like bathroom with split vanities, a soaking tub, separate standing shower & the frosted glass window & shower door add artistic touches to the already stunning bathroom. The backyard and porch are perfect for entertaining and are fully fenced!
